{"tid":449286,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"開騷唱《美少女戰士》　周慧敏唔着女團衫","createTime":"2017-10-27T05:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T05:41:46.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8418d3a687aefd74ad9f4e3a9f79d6ddbbc7b10","tid":449286,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171026/photo/bkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171026193159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171026193159&h=3fa3bd2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手周慧敏（Vivian）到台北香堤大道廣場出席無綫「大大平台正式上線」記者會，問到明年一月演唱會的籌備進度，她表示11月8或9日才開始綵排。<br />\n<br />\nVivian稱現時忙於與製作團隊開會商討個唱詳情，更透露會有跳舞環節，希望有新的視覺效果及新鮮感帶給觀眾。問到有沒有請嘉賓，她說：「淨係講咗《美少女戰士》（同王馨平和湯寶如合唱），因為嗰隻歌係要還債，好似欠咗大家，計劃咗會喺個騷都唱，將經典重演，唔想好草率咁做。（着番嗰套衫？）暫時我唔想着，啲衫好女團感覺，我覺得唔適合，我哋係成熟嘅婦人，做番女性嘅打扮。但世事冇絕對，可能有人話想着。」她又謂今次極力爭取粉絲想聽，但平時大家少聽到的歌。<br />\n<br />\n此外，Vivian透露好友古巨基私下已幫她設計服飾，但最後會由她作最後決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171026/photo/bkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_02b.jpg?20171026193159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20171026193159&h=8b5941a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171026/photo/bkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_05b.jpg?20171026193159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20171026193159&h=ba4176d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171026/bkn-20171026184854189-1026_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2